{"title":"修理小队","authors":["钟毅岗"],"dates":[{"year":1963,"month":4,"day":7}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"修理小队"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钟毅岗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东山一声呼唤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"西山两脚飞梭；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多快好省的步子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踏出欢乐的漩涡——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"路上破车复新，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"载着累累金禾；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田间病犁受诊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"犁出满垅欢乐……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挑起，欢歌满口，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"落下，小店一个；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一腔兄弟的赤诚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一根情谊的脉搏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"涌进社里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连着心窝……。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}